tip.text: Great ambience, delicious vegetarian food! And superb coffee as well... Very happy indeed.
Mr Gan is very friendly, passionate about the quality of his work and delivers on time. Very reasonably priced as well. Highly recommended for all car body repair works including spray painting.
Outstandingly good idli, medu vadai and thosai (dosa), as well as delicious chutneys and sambhar to go with! Spot on.
Thosai is good and the appam is even better.. Lovely clean restaurant as well, a great find.
The einkorn pancakes are delicious, as are the vegetarian sausages!
